These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, dancing, reading
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, british, french
3 different games are played: snooker, whist, poker
There 3 different types of food: cranberry, plum, artichoke
1. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is between the british and the french##2
4. the person eating cranberry is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person playing poker is the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | dancing | baking   | reading   |
| Nationality   | british     | pakistani | french |
| Game   | poker  | snooker    | whist      |
| Food     | plum     | cranberry      | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-2::.
There 3 different types of food: kale, raspberry, tomato
City: rome, edinburgh, liverpool
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, fisherman, mechanic
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, cola, lemonade
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
2. the mechanic is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person eating raspberry is the mechanic##1
4. the person eating kale is the fisherman##1
5. the person drinking juice is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person eating tomato##2
6. the person eating tomato is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |
| Food          | raspberry  | kale     | tomato     |
| City   | edinburgh     | liverpool     | rome      |
| Job   | mechanic  | fisherman | accountant |
| Beverage           | lemonade | juice     | cola       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: pop, punk, disco
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, december, august
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, go, domino
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, snake
1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person playing domino##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person playing domino##2
3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is the fan of punk##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre          | pop  | disco     | punk     |
| Birthday           | august | may  | december   |
| Game   | mah-jongg  | go    | domino |
| Pet           | snake     | chinchilla | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-4::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, cucumber, raspberry
City: hamburg, rome, venice
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, chess, writing
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, orchid, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
3. the person eating raspberry is between the person traveling to rome and the person who's hobby is photography##2
4. the person eating cucumber is the person who growsorchid##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Food    | cherry       | raspberry  | cucumber   |
| City     | rome    | venice  | hamburg |
| Hobby     | chess   | writing | photography        |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | iris     | orchid      |

