2. the owner of the bird is between the person driving the taxi and the person who growsorchid##2
3. the person who growsbegonia is the owner of the dog##1
4. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the cottage house##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| House          | cottage    | gothic-revival     | futuristic      |
| Flower         | begonia | zinnia | orchid |
| Transport   | taxi  | ship       | airplane       |
