2. the person who growslily is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
3. the person driving the roller is between the person who growszinnia and the person traveling to london##2
4. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |
| Flower          | zinnia | marigold | lily    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | sudoku      | filmmaking |
| Transport   | subway   | roller     | van        |
| City           | miami      | rome       | london      |

