The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, fishing, skydiving
3 different pets are kept: pony, hedgehog, frog
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, dahlia, daffodil
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who growsmarigold##2
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the owner of the pony##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3     |
| Beverage          | soy-milk      | fanta   | sprite |
| Hobby         | board-games | fishing | skydiving |
| Pet   | pony      | frog | hedgehog   |
| Flower     | daffodil         | dahlia  | marigold       |

