.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-8::.
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, corn, lettuce
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, cooking, zombie-climbing
There are 3 different favourite colors: amber, grey, turquise
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, superhero, zombie
1. the person who likes turquise is on the far left##1
2. the person eating corn is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person eating corn is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person who likes amber is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person eating lettuce##2
5. the person eating corn is the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |     3      |
| Food      | pomegranate       | corn      | lettuce      |
| Hobby         | cooking    | zombie-climbing | chess      |
| Color           | turquise | amber     | grey |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero     | zombie          | time-travel       |

