3. the fan of blues is the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is the social-worker##1
5. the person playing whist is on the left of the engineer##1
6. the person playing snooker is the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |        2        |    3     |
