There 3 different types of food: corn, pear, carrot
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the person eating corn is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person traveling to marseilles##2
6. the person traveling to hannover is the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |       3        |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | iced-tea      | tea            |
| Sport           | swimming | baseball | volleyball |
| City   | marseilles     | new-york        | hannover         |
| Food   | pear  | corn    | carrot        |

