The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, zinnia, tulip
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, fisherman, police-officer
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, swisher, tiparillo
1. the person driving the tram is between the swisher-smoker and the person who growstulip##2
2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the coach##1
3. the police-officer is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
4. the person who growstulip is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is the swisher-smoker##1
6. the coach is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |       3       |
| Transport      | roller    | tram          | motorbike |
| Flower          | tulip | zinnia           | daisy        |
| Job           | fisherman | police-officer | coach         |
| Cigar   | havana    | tiparillo    | swisher      |

