3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking tea is the entrepreneur##1
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the entrepreneur##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |      3       |
| Hobby       | singing | gardening | magic-tricks |
