.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, electronic, folk
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, soy-milk, water
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, family, time-travel
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, october, august
1. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person drinking tea##2
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the fan of electronic is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is the fan of disco##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is the person watching family movies##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | disco  | folk     |
| Beverage   | water    | soy-milk | tea |
| Movie-Genre           | martial-arts        | time-travel   | family  |
| Birthday     | august      | october   | december |

