.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-19::.
House: wooden, tower, colonial
3 different games are played: domino, backgammon, canasta
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, reggae, techno
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is rowing is the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
3. the fan of disco is between the wooden house and the person playing domino##2
4. the fan of reggae is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person who's sport is badminton is between the tower house and the fan of reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |
| House      | wooden | colonial     | tower        |
| Game         | backgammon   | canasta | domino |
| Music-Genre   | reggae        | disco       | techno      |
| Sport           | lacrosse           | badminton    | rowing       |

