.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-2-20::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, photographer, dressmaker
3 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, rabbit
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, writing, filmmaking
City: boston, rome, marseilles
1. the manager is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is the dressmaker##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person who's hobby is writing##2
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Job        | photographer      | manager | dressmaker |
| Pet         | goldfish     | rabbit    | dog        |
| Hobby       | writing | filmmaking   | singing   |
| City   | boston          | rome     | marseilles       |

 